The EV Point application was created for the most comfortable use of the EV Point Moldova charging station network  Our application will help you to:
- Find the nearest station;
- Check station's status online;
- Reserve the station;
- Easily identify the station with QR code;
- Start the charging process;
- Continuously monitor the charging process;
- Stop the charging process;
- Top up the balance in your personal account with a bank card;
- Access the full history of charging sessions;
- Access the account balance history ;
- Contact technical support.

Do you still think that changing the plan is hard, and you have to contact an operator to deactivate a service? Start using My Kyivstar app and get free megabytes, minutes or other bonuses for the first installation.

With the app, you can:

- find out about promotions and special offers;
- keep track of how many megabytes, minutes and SMS you have used;
- top up accounts without commission for yourself or your loved ones;
- change your plan yourself;
- activate useful services and deactivate the ones you don't need;
- analyze your expenses by categories or periods.

At that's not all! My Kyivstar is getting better with every update.

Have you found a bug in the app? Do you know which feature is missing in the program? We are looking forward to your letters: apps@kyivstar.net.
